name: Chinese zodiac series (monkey)
description:
Zodiac Monkey has a sharp personality, smart, but a little mischievous.

People born in the year of the Monkey are magnetic, funny, and intelligent.

With a slightly childish nature, curiosity, and intelligence make these Monkeys very naughty.
The Monkey zodiac sign was born in 1956, 1968, 1980, 1992, 2004, 2016, and 2018.
